#. type: Plain text
#: upstream/_guides/redis-reference.adoc:17
#, fuzzy
msgid "As the list of commands which are supported out-of-box by both https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/blob/main/extensions/redis-client/runtime/src/main/java/io/quarkus/redis/client/RedisClient.java[`RedisClient`] and https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/blob/main/extensions/redis-client/runtime/src/main/java/io/quarkus/redis/client/reactive/ReactiveRedisClient.java[`ReactiveRedisClient`] depends on what is available in https://github.com/vert-x3/vertx-redis-client[`vertx-redis-client`], then there might be case when you need a command which is not (yet) available via https://github.com/vert-x3/vertx-redis-client[`vertx-redis-client`]."
msgstr "の両方でサポートされているコマンドのリストは、以下の通りです。  link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/blob/main/extensions/redis-client/runtime/src/main/java/io/quarkus/redis/client/RedisClient.java[`RedisClient`]と  link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/blob/main/extensions/redis-client/runtime/src/main/java/io/quarkus/redis/client/reactive/ReactiveRedisClient.java[`ReactiveRedisClient`]で利用可能なものに依存します。  link:https://github.com/vert-x3/vertx-redis-client[`vertx-redis-client`]で利用可能なものに依存するため、場合によっては  link:https://github.com/vert-x3/vertx-redis-client[`vertx-redis-client`]."

#. type: Plain text
#: upstream/_guides/redis-reference.adoc:20
#, fuzzy
msgid "In such case (if you don't want to wait for the new command to be supported in https://github.com/vert-x3/vertx-redis-client[`vertx-redis-client`]), you can implement it in either https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/blob/main/extensions/redis-client/runtime/src/main/java/io/quarkus/redis/client/RedisClient.java[`RedisClient`] or https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/blob/main/extensions/redis-client/runtime/src/main/java/io/quarkus/redis/client/reactive/ReactiveRedisClient.java[`ReactiveRedisClient`].  In order to do so, you will need:"
msgstr "このような場合（新しいコマンドがサポートされるのを待ちたくない場合  link:https://github.com/vert-x3/vertx-redis-client[`vertx-redis-client`]でサポートされるのを待ちたくない場合）は、次のいずれかで実装できます。  link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/blob/main/extensions/redis-client/runtime/src/main/java/io/quarkus/redis/client/RedisClient.java[`RedisClient`]または  link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/blob/main/extensions/redis-client/runtime/src/main/java/io/quarkus/redis/client/reactive/ReactiveRedisClient.java[`ReactiveRedisClient`].そのためには、以下のものが必要となります。"

#. type: Plain text
#: upstream/_guides/redis-reference.adoc:22
#, fuzzy
msgid "Generate a new `Command` based on the nodejs code available in https://github.com/vert-x3/vertx-redis-client[`vertx-redis-client`] repository:"
msgstr "で公開されているnodejsのコードに基づいて、新しい `Command` を生成します。  link:https://github.com/vert-x3/vertx-redis-client[`vertx-redis-client`]リポジトリを使用しています。"

#. type: Plain text
#: upstream/_guides/redis-reference.adoc:24
#, fuzzy
msgid "If you don't have a Redis service running locally, you can run Redis in a Docker container:"
msgstr "Redisのサービスをローカルで実行していない場合は、DockerコンテナでRedisを実行することができます。"

#. type: delimited block -
#: upstream/_guides/redis-reference.adoc:27
#, no-wrap
msgid "docker run --name redis -p 7006:6379 -d redis\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: upstream/_guides/redis-reference.adoc:30
#, fuzzy
msgid "Next, while being in https://github.com/vert-x3/vertx-redis-client[`vertx-redis-client`] root folder execute:"
msgstr "次に、ルートフォルダにいる状態で  link:https://github.com/vert-x3/vertx-redis-client[`vertx-redis-client`]ルートフォルダを実行します。"

#. type: delimited block -
#: upstream/_guides/redis-reference.adoc:36
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"cd tools\n"
"npm i\n"
"npm start\n"
msgstr ""

